An over-long map literal in a declaration with no gsx element anywhere. The
break rule is not element-gated: fmtGoChunk hands breakWideLiterals an empty
forceMarker (there are no gsx holes to force a break for), and the pass still
breaks this map's entries one per line purely on measured width.

-- input.gsx --
package ui

var labels = map[string]string{"home": "Home Dashboard Overview", "import": "Import and Export Data", "users": "User Management Console"}
-- fmt.golden --
package ui

var labels = map[string]string{
	"home":   "Home Dashboard Overview",
	"import": "Import and Export Data",
	"users":  "User Management Console",
}
